==English==
===Etymology===
See the Wikipedia article [[w:ISO 216|ISO 216]], the international standard on paper sizes.

===Noun===
'''A8'''
# A standard [[paper]] size, defined by ISO 216.
#: dimensions: 74 x 53 mm  (74.325 x 52.556 mm)

===Adjective===
'''A8'''
# of that size
#:  ''a sheet of '''A8''' paper''

